webpackJsonp([0x6e7db7453485],{727:function(e,n){e.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p>Common responses provide consistent messaging across the platform and prevent you from having to write out the same message again and again. When you select an action for a report, you can have a common response pre-populate for that specific action.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/common-response-1-ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6-0b548.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 52%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="common-response-1"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/common-response-1-ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/common-response-1-ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6-67829.png 125w,\n/static/common-response-1-ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/common-response-1-ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/common-response-1-ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/common-response-1-ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/common-response-1-ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6-b3ac4.png 1500w,\n/static/common-response-1-ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6-0b548.png 2400w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>[Set Up a Default Common Response](#set-up-a-default-common-response)</h3>\nTo set a default common response:\n1. Go to **Settings > Program > Automation > Common Responses**.\n2. You\'ll find a pre-populated list of responses that HackerOne finds useful.\n3. Click the **Set default Common Responses** button.\n4. In the **Default Common Responses** window, select the default response message from the drop-down next to the action.\n5. Click **Save**.\n<p>The default common response will automatically populate when you select the action for the report.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/common-response-2-b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d-b3cba.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 493px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 142.59634888438134%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="common-response-2"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/common-response-2-b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d-b3cba.png"\n        srcset="/static/common-response-2-b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d-1f5ec.png 125w,\n/static/common-response-2-b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d-c025f.png 250w,\n/static/common-response-2-b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d-b3cba.png 493w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>[Add Your Own Common Response](#add-your-own-common-response)</h3>\nYou can write your own common response\nTo add a new common response:\n1. Go to **Settings > Program > Automation > Common Responses**.\n2. Select the **Add Common Response** button. \n3. Type the title of your response in the **Common Response Title** field. This title will show up in the list of common responses to choose from.\n4. Type the message of your response in the **Message** field.\n5. Click **Create Common Response**.\n<p>Your common response will display in the list of common responses to choose from when you set up a default common response.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/common-response-3-5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372-b9fe5.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 72.67759562841529%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="common-response-3"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/common-response-3-5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372-2f183.png"\n        srcset="/static/common-response-3-5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372-67829.png 125w,\n/static/common-response-3-5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372-5c59f.png 250w,\n/static/common-response-3-5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372-2f183.png 500w,\n/static/common-response-3-5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372-c93e8.png 750w,\n/static/common-response-3-5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372-4e628.png 1000w,\n/static/common-response-3-5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372-b9fe5.png 1464w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3>[Edit a Common Response](#edit-a-common-response)</h3>\nTo edit a common response:\n1. Go to **Settings > Program > Automation > Common Responses**.\n2. Click the title of the response you want to edit.\n3. Edit the title and the message.\n4. Click **Update Common Response**.',frontmatter:{path:"/programs/common-responses.html",id:"programs/common-responses",title:"Common Responses",description:null}}},pathContext:{}}}});
